	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> habuimus literas, inter quas quidam <persName ref="p18113" cert="high">Mecardus</persName> nomine, qui illic adhuc strenue praedicat de concilio, talia scribit, quae quoniam forte tibi non erunt ingrata cognitu, transscribam huc: "De concilio nihil, quod scribam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Doctor <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18137">Marpachius</persName> (est is <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinensis</placeName> ecclesiae minister) fuit <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1678" cert="high">Niddae</placeName> apud <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p9046" cert="high">Pistorium</persName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l664" cert="high">Hassia</placeName>, fuit <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Franckfordię</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l284" cert="high">Lipsiae</placeName>, <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Wittenbergae</placeName>, apud Ioannem marchionem et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l361" cert="high">Norinbergę</placeName>; sic scribit ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20811" cert="high">Ascanium</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name">regis Angliae</persName> legatum, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8121" cert="high">Montius</persName> atque inter alia: Nova hic nulla habemus praeterquam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2095" cert="high">Melanchthonem</persName> modo conscribere confessionem fidei earum ecclesiarum, quae evangelium per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniam</placeName> profitentur.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Similiter <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentius</persName> et <persName ref="p1055" cert="high">Frechtus</persName> nostrorum theologorum opera in eodem argumento laborant, ut ex his conscriptionibus collatis et recognitis una tandem absoluta confessio, quae omnium nostrorum theologorum assensu et iudicio exhibeatur in concilio (si quod fuerit) et fidei nostrae ratio coram universo mundo reddatur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et si praeterea papa nostros volet iniquis abusibus, temerariis praeiudiciis et usurpatis superstitionibus tyrannice premere, ut tum declinationes, accusationes, exceptiones et omnis generis defensiones opponant et protestentur tam contra suspectum, imo inimicum et hostilem iudicem quam contra universum iudicium, quod in propria causa cognitionem, accusationem et condemnationem sibi contra fas et leges arrogantissime vendicet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ille."</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Scripsit et alias post illas priores <persName ref="p18113" cert="high">Mecardus</persName> ad <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculum</persName> literas, in quibus haec habet: <foreign xml:lang="de">"Mir ist den 1. tag augsten überschickt worden ein copy deß convents zuͦ <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Wittemberg</placeName>, den 5. iulii gehalten, da alle gelerten beider universiteten, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l284" cert="high">Leiptzig</placeName> und <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Wittenberg</placeName>, sampt allen superintendenten beider fürsten, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18250">Moritzen</persName> und <persName type="citizen_name">Augusti</persName>, und ist ein confession von <persName type="auto_name">Philippo</persName> gstellt, examiniert, approbiert und von allen subscribiert worden,</foreign> quae offeretur in concilio futuro, cui <persName type="citizen_name">Iohannis, marchionis Brandenburgensis</persName>, ministri subscripsere, item <persName type="citizen_name">ducis Pomeranię</persName> et <persName type="citizen_name">ducis Meckelburgensis</persName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Faciunt quoque in fine mentionem civitatis <placeName type="auto_name">Nerobergensis</placeName> et <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratensis</placeName>, quod et ipsae huic sint subscripturae.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec habui ad concilium pertinentia.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustae</placeName> geratur, te non puto ignorare; scripsit <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blaurerus</persName> quaedam ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1754">Iungium</persName> quae sine dubio tibi quoque prius communicavit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="de">Der renntmeister ist wider verhanden,</foreign> forte iam est vobiscum; a quo cognosces mira.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916">Schertli</persName> ist in anstößen <placeName ref="l631" cert="high">Burgund</placeName> und <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Franckrych</placeName>; weiß nitt, was vorhanden ist.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Haec satis importuno tempore scripsi, ne omnino nihil scriberem per hunc doctissimum et optimum virum, fratrem nostrum d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Theodorum Bezam</persName>, qui valde vestras desiderat videre facies; eum tibi et reliquis fratribus omnibus commendo, quos ex me salutabis.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant vos quoque nostri, praesertim <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName>, cuius venter fluere nondum desiit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 15. augusti sub crepusculum vespertinum.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus, quem nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae antistiti fidelissimo, domino et compatri charissimo suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
